These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, camping
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, designer
1. the videographer is in an even position##4
2. the designer is the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | camping | fishing |
| Job     | designer    | videographer   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, surfing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda        |
| Sport      | badminton  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, indie
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, pakistani
1. the chinese is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa |
| Nationality   | chinese | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: cola, juice
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, apricot
1. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person eating apricot is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | cola      | juice |
| Food       | kiwi | apricot    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
