 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding
The people use 2 different means of transport: train, boat
1. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Sport       | skateboarding | biathlon  |
| Transport   | boat  | train |

